// ProjectDeliveryS139 — Sprint 139: scaffoldCommitGate (D0093) — `keel init` scaffolds a RUST-ONLY
// pre-commit gate (.githooks/pre-commit running keel validate + guard; no conda/JVM) so a downstream
// project has an automated gate from day one. Live-verified: the scaffolded gate rejected a bad .sysml
// commit with zero conda. 2 pts. AUTONOMOUS (D0049).
